@prefix rdf:         <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs:        <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix sh:          <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#> .
@prefix xsd:         <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix schema:      <http://schema.org/>.
@prefix dcterms:     <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>.
@prefix cdifd: <https://cdif.org/validation/0.1/shacl#> .
@base <https://www.ogc.org/rules/template/> .

# DDE conformsTo constraint is enforced by:
# - JSON Schema: contains constraint on dcterms:conformsTo requiring ddeCore URI
# - Profile-level SHACL: each DDE profile shape checks schema:subjectOf -> dcterms:conformsTo
# No BB-level SHACL shape needed here since the catalog record is validated
# as a nested node within full dataset documents at the profile level.
